{"tid":1926514,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英女王「擔心感染」：已逃離白金漢宮","createTime":"2020-03-15T07:23:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T12:56:33.000Z","uid":226548,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7730f0c6147a95beaa299961541eec076be1951e","tid":1926514,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YuaPGaU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYuaPGaU.jpg&h=9ac9c64d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》今（15）日最新消息，因擔心感染新冠病毒，英國女王已離開白金漢宮前往溫莎城堡。報道稱，如疫情進一步擴散，女王將與丈夫菲臘親王前往桑德靈厄姆府（Sandringham House）。<br />\n<br />\n另據美媒報道，特朗普政府宣布正在擴大針對來自歐洲旅客的旅行限制，將英國和愛爾蘭也包括在內。目前全球各國正爭相採取措施，以遏制疫情蔓延，並減輕經濟影響。（編輯：李袁木）"},{"pid":"8f6a2010d3d62ad812475a46178f5148e01b8575","tid":1926514,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:24:17.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.exmoo.com/article/143877.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.exmoo.com%2Farticle%2F143877.html&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOyQESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=adefc3d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.exmoo.com/article/143877.html</a>"},{"pid":"1aa1676f0a01ccdc219f5928c92fd170356dead3","tid":1926514,"uid":20170,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:25:26.000Z","msg":"意思姐係，女王都覺得BJ癡閪線"},{"pid":"99fb03f39b3fb91bb9fc3935d1f4632fae568bda","tid":1926514,"uid":66087,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:27:25.000Z","msg":"BJ: 全民感染，全民抗體<br />\n<br />\nQueen: 彩你都傻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e20c401ff74ee50fd973d1123e99b18caeb941","tid":1926514,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:28:31.000Z","msg":"习腫咁都無事證明隻嘢係人造"},{"pid":"7cc99f2c73302421cb44d36a15